text: Grächen is a municipality of the district of Visp in the canton of Valais in Switzerland. It is at an elevation of on a terrace above St. Niklaus in the Mattertal, north of the Mischabel range (and Dom). ==Gallery== File:Grächenkirche.JPG|Church of Grächen File:Grächen.jpg|Grächen File:Hannigalp.jpg|Hannigalp File:Grächen town.jpg|Houses near Grächen ==References== ==Other websites== * Official website of the municipality of Grächen * information. * Category:Municipalities in Visp
